-- Fed’s Bernanke to Be Interviewed Today by ABC News’ Diane Sawyer
-- B y   J o s h u a   Z u m b r u n
-- 2012-03-27T14:55:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-27/fed-s-bernanke-to-be-interviewed-today-by-abc-news-diane-sawyer.html
Federal Reserve Chairman  Ben S. Bernanke  will be interviewed today by ABC News anchor  Diane Sawyer , according to a release from the network.  “With signs that the economy is moving in the right
direction, Sawyer will talk to Bernanke to get the whole picture
on the current state of the United States economy and the buying
power Americans have in their wallets,” ABC said in a
statement.  The interview will air on “World News with Diane Sawyer”
at 6:30 p.m. on the ABC Television Network.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Joshua Zumbrun in Washington at 
 jzumbrun@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
